data.description: Open houses: Saturday 12/2 from 1-4pm and Sunday 12/3 from 1-4pm!   **THE SALE OF THIS HOME OFFERS A MEMBERSHIP TO THE TPC GOLF CLUB AT THE JW MARRIOTT FOR A TRANSFER FEE OF ONLY $2,500-- There is currently a closed waitlist, so this is the only way to become a member immediately, and this transfer of ownership saves you the $35,000 initiation fee!! Please inquire for additional details.**    This stunning 4 bedroom 3.5 bathroom home has been impeccably maintained and is ready for the next family to enjoy it! Primary bedroom is located downstairs and 3 additional bedrooms plus a large game room are all upstairs. This home features an incredible laundry room that doubles as a craft/hobby room with tons of built in storage. Yard backs up to a private green space, so you can enjoy peaceful evenings sitting on the large covered deck. Resort-style neighborhood amenities include multiple pools, a clubhouse and a gym. Home is located less than a mile from the beautiful JW Marriott. Brand new roof installed June 2023.
